  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims to reduce deforestation and enhance restoration of forests and natural vegetation in Brazil by improving protection of primary and secondary vegetation, increasing agricultural production without increased deforestation, create policy incentives to drive land use changes that align production and conservation, incorporate safeguards against deforestation in Brazilian infrstaructure planning.</narrative>
